title: Cat Donut Test - TOY TEST
description:
Another cat toy test with Fabius and Viego. This time it is a giant donut, the perfect place to hide. 

On this channel, I test cat toys to see how much fun my cats have with them. Fabius and Viego always get excited about new toys and are usually thrilled right from the start!

If you'd like to see more tests and cat challenges, feel free to leave a like and follow the channel.
